4
00:00:20.329 --> 00:00:22.729
To manage the immense weight of the IT

5
00:00:22.729 --> 00:00:25.950
gear within the expanded 1200 millimeter width,

6
00:00:26.370 --> 00:00:26.870
ORW

7
00:00:27.250 --> 00:00:30.670
utilizes a unique mechanical substructure

8
00:00:30.920 --> 00:00:32.110
