9
00:00:32.900 --> 00:00:36.479
This heavily reinforced chassis ensures rigid support

10
00:00:36.880 --> 00:00:41.520
and precise alignment as the massive server nodes slide into the rack.

11
00:00:41.979 --> 00:00:45.000
This mechanical precision is absolutely critical.

12
00:00:46.279 --> 00:00:48.619
To extract the massive heat load.

13
00:00:49.689 --> 00:00:53.659
Thick vertical cooling manifolds are mounted securely into

14
00:00:53.659 --> 00:00:56.779
