22
00:01:18.239 --> 00:01:20.620
As the canister slides into the rack,

23
00:01:20.839 --> 00:01:25.239
the PBMC system automatically aligns the fluid connectors.

24
00:01:25.720 --> 00:01:28.540
It utilizes a brilliant mechanical pivot

25
00:01:28.720 --> 00:01:33.069
to absorb the extreme weight and positional tolerance of the hardware,

26
00:01:33.440 --> 00:01:37.919
